paragraphs.text: Usually a fan of F&F, but was kinda disappointed with “Fate”, and the whole franchise is starting to look repetitive and like it’s sorta “jumped the shark”. Or maybe just time for Dom to ‘retire’…. except he’s all that’s still holding it together.
